			<h3 ><a href="#p26716"></a></h3>

									<ul class="post-buttons">
																																									<li>
							<a href="./posting.php?mode=quote&amp;f=34&amp;p=26716&amp;sid=a9115b02160979be105304736ea08a1f" title="Ответить с цитатой" class="button icon-button quote-icon"><span>Цитата</span></a>
